ible. </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Integral to this </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">is</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> both product developm</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ent and </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">the </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">promotion of the sport</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> to new audiences. </span></li></ol><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="29" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">The LTA has </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">established</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> a working group which has been tasked with developing a long term strategy to raise the profile of women and girls’ participation in tennis. The ove</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">rall w</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">omen </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">and g</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">irls programme of work includes various work streams</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">, including</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> young girls, teenagers, mum</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">s and women aged 35+. While </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">the LTA has</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> generic insight into the barriers and opportunities to getting more women and girls playing tennis, this insight isn’t </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">yet </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">specifi</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">c to the different age groups and known </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">drop off points.</span></li></ol><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="30" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">As part of our initial work </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">stream on increasing the number of women playing more often, we have recently commissioned a small piece of qualitative research </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">that will explore</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> the reasons why women aged 21 - 34 only play tennis infrequently or have lapsed playing, and what will really</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> encourage them to play more often. This research will enable us to develop an informed offer for this particular group, and we will look to follow a similar insight led approach when developing campaigns for other key groups.</span></li></ol><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="31" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">In relation to products</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> deve</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">lopment</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">the LTA and partners have worked to create a range of products that takes tennis and adapts it </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">to modern lifestyle demands. This includes </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">a product called Cardio Tennis. </span></li></ol><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="32" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Cardio Tennis is a programme that combines an aerobic workout with tennis d</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">rills. Sessions usually last for an hour with six to 12 players running around the court taking turns to hit balls fed by a qualified tennis coach.  </span></li></ol><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="33" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">The research that has been undertaken shows that the average 150 lb. person burns 350 calories playing </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">doubles tennis for an hour, rising to 460 calories for singles tennis.  With Cardio Tennis participants can burn in</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> excess of 700 calories an hour. </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span></li></ol><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="34" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Over 700 facilities across Britain already offer the </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">programme, and t</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">he</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> feedback </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">the LTA has captured</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">to date </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">shows that</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> of the 12,000 regular weekly participants,</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> 75% </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">existing </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> are female, with women 35+ identified as the main target demographic.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> The product is seen as a fun, social, and active format of the game. </span></li></ol><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="35" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Our aim to raise awareness of tennis am</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ongst women has been reflected in a more targeted media and PR strategy focused on consumer media to directly reach women. We have worked with inspiring role models from the sport such as the GB’s women’s team (Fed Cup team) and famous faces</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> (Kirsty Gallac</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">her and Gaby Logan, TV presenters)</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> to help promote tennis in women’s, lifestyle, fitness and other consumer media, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">as well as</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> national print, on-line and broadcast</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">. </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">We work</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> with media to show how women can get back into tennis or take up the sport for the </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">first time. One example is a competition we ran with Women’</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">s Weekly to provide women </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">around the country with the opportunity to try out Cardio Tennis for free over 10 weeks and write about it via the publication and its social media channels. </span></li></ol><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="36" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">We have als</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">o run events</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> specifically targeted at women</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> to </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">give them the opportunity to </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">try out the sport. </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Our promotion of</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> Cardio Tennis in January 2013 </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">involved </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">an event at Westfield Shopping Centre </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">– part of their MY2013 women’s lifestyle promotion - </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">with a specifi</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">c aim of encouraging women to try out the product. We chose Westfield as the demographic was closely aligned to one of the target audiences for Cardio Tennis – women aged over 35</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">, and t</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">he event was a great success with </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">approximately 700 participants </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">trying out the Cardio Tennis activity. </span></li></ol><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="37" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">To inform our plans going forward, we are actively engaging organisations such as the Women’s Spor</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">t and Fitness Foundation (WSFF)</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> including their </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">“She Moves”</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> campaign</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">the </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Women’s