tiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Supported more than </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">16,700</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> schools across Great Britai</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">n with free teacher training, resources and equipment, with the vast majority being state schools; </span></p><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">-</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Provided training to </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">29</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">,000+</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> teachers and coaches to help them deliver tennis in schools; </span></p><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">-</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Increased the number of children taking part in school team compe</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">titions – last year more than </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">50,664</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> pupils took part in a schools tennis competition with </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">secondary competition up 14%</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> in last two years alone; </span></p><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">-</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Boosted links between schools and clubs and community tennis facilities</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">and will continue to grow this </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">through our plans to establish 200 Tennis Satellite Clubs on school sites over the next f</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">our years</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">; </span></p><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">-</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">We recently </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">commissioned</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> YouGov </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">to carry out an impact </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">survey of our schools </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">programme,</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">with 98% of schools responding saying the programme had overwhelmingly resulted in their school delivering tennis or more tennis. </span></p><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">-</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">95% of schools who took part in the survey (1,335 schools) are drawn </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">from the state sector and the vast majority (95%) agree </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">that the programme </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">is</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> helping to make tennis more inclusive and accessible for their pupils.</span></p><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="40" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Aegon Schools Tennis has been designed as a programme for teachers to use in the curriculum, with a whole class at a time. Therefore, it’s a fair assumption that </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">it will be a fairly equal split in terms of gender.</span></li></ol><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="41" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">The Tennis Foundation and LTA work closely with the </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">partners such as the </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Youth Sport Trust, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">other </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">sporting f</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">oundations (such as Tottenham Hotspur Football Foundation</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> in Haringey</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">) and </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">a range of </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">charity a</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">nd community organisations</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> to </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">extend our </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">reach </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">and </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">provide opportunities for girls to play tennis</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">, including for example </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">the Greenhouse </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Charity</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">.  </span></li></ol><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="42" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Greenhouse is a charity</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">that works with </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">young people in London's disadvantaged communities to realise their </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">potential through high quality, intensive sport and dance programmes delivered by coaches</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">. </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Our partnership with Greenhouse in Tower Hamlets at St. Paul’s Way</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> School</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> has the highest female participation across all their</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> programmes across all sports, with th</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">e p</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ercentage of girls involved in Greenhouse programme </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">currently at</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> 35%. </span></li></ol><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="43" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-