Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> Year 1 of the programme (Sept 13 to Sept 14).</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="45" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">The Tennis Foundation and LTA also run an initiative called Aegon </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Schools </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Team </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">T</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ennis, which </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">is a team </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">based </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">competition that aims to provide players </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">with regular league matches </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">against similar standard playe</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">rs in a </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">competitive team environment. </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">The recent figures for Team Tennis Schools Year 8&amp;10 were the following:</span></li></ol><p style="line-height:12.5pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:1